WEBVTT

00:00:00.126 --> 00:00:03.756 A:middle
The Companion tab displays
text, interactive tasks,

00:00:03.756 --> 00:00:07.076 A:middle
and instructions to guide
you through each project.

00:00:07.206 --> 00:00:10.406 A:middle
It contains guidance for
using the code editor;

00:00:10.466 --> 00:00:14.066 A:middle
the required tasks for the
assignment; and instructions

00:00:14.066 --> 00:00:15.836 A:middle
for how to complete
the assignment.

00:00:15.926 --> 00:00:19.336 A:middle
It also includes an
example output for the task.

00:00:19.616 --> 00:00:22.046 A:middle
To run your code
in the code editor,

00:00:22.046 --> 00:00:24.816 A:middle
simply select the
Run Code button.

00:00:25.036 --> 00:00:26.916 A:middle
This will execute the code

00:00:26.916 --> 00:00:30.656 A:middle
and show you the output
while identifying any errors

00:00:30.726 --> 00:00:31.816 A:middle
that may have occurred.

00:00:31.896 --> 00:00:34.666 A:middle
To check if tasks have
met the requirements,

00:00:34.936 --> 00:00:37.296 A:middle
select the Calculate
Grade button.

00:00:37.576 --> 00:00:39.846 A:middle
If the tasks have
been fulfilled,

00:00:39.996 --> 00:00:41.846 A:middle
a green checkmark will appear.

00:00:42.026 --> 00:00:44.386 A:middle
If the tasks have
not been fulfilled,

00:00:44.386 --> 00:00:47.016 A:middle
a red X will appear instead.

00:00:47.256 --> 00:00:50.986 A:middle
Continue to refine, run,
and calculate your code

00:00:51.056 --> 00:00:53.276 A:middle
until you are satisfied
with the outcome.

00:00:53.446 --> 00:00:56.916 A:middle
To submit the assignment,
select the Submit button.

